60|$|Julia could rejoice {{that he was}} gone. His {{presence}} was beginning to be odious to her; and if Maria gained him not, she was now cool enough to dispense with any other revenge. She did not want exposure {{to be added to}} desertion. Henry Crawford gone, <b>she</b> <b>could</b> <b>even</b> pity her sister.|$|E
